WEBVTT

00:08.471 --> 00:09.008
Hi.

00:09.009 --> 00:11.743
Hi.

00:11.745 --> 00:13.111
Okay.

00:16.649 --> 00:18.416
So I thought we'd...
try this new restaurant.

00:18.418 --> 00:20.018
It's right around
the corner from here.

00:20.020 --> 00:21.686
It's Scottish-Mexican fusion.

00:21.688 --> 00:23.088
Scottish-Mexican fusion?

00:23.090 --> 00:24.689
Scottish-Mexican fusion.

00:24.691 --> 00:27.192
That would seem like two things
that do not fuse.

00:27.194 --> 00:28.793
Perhaps you'll change
your mind when you try

00:28.795 --> 00:30.362
their signature
haggis enchiladas.

00:30.364 --> 00:31.730
Okay.

00:31.732 --> 00:34.466
All right. Yeah, come on.
Lead the way.

00:34.468 --> 00:37.302
I was surprised
when you called.

00:37.304 --> 00:38.670
Isn't there some
universal guy rule

00:38.672 --> 00:41.239
where you have to wait
four days to call a girl?

00:41.241 --> 00:43.274
That... does not ring a bell.

00:43.276 --> 00:44.609
And it's three days.

00:45.879 --> 00:47.278
Here we are.

00:49.516 --> 00:52.117
Uh, I did not realize
there would be live music.

00:52.119 --> 00:54.452
So, uh, should we...

00:54.454 --> 00:55.620
Eat anywhere but here?

00:55.622 --> 00:57.288
Yeah. Yeah.
Yeah. Yeah.

00:57.290 --> 00:58.957
Besides, I'm sure
we can find a place

00:58.959 --> 01:00.125
where we don't need
reservations.

01:00.127 --> 01:01.593
Oh, you think
it's just that easy?

01:01.595 --> 01:03.828
Just stroll in off the
street and get a meal?

01:03.830 --> 01:07.766
Well, let me tell you
the tale of Gary Blauman.

01:07.768 --> 01:09.300
There's the blushing bride!

01:09.302 --> 01:10.802
Oh!

01:10.804 --> 01:12.103
Gary Blauman!

01:12.105 --> 01:13.638
How are you?!

01:13.640 --> 01:15.573
Uh, duh, like I need to ask.

01:15.575 --> 01:16.875
You're getting married.

01:16.877 --> 01:19.177
Well, don't let me keep you.
You have things to do.

01:19.179 --> 01:21.913
I will see you
walking down the aisle.

01:21.915 --> 01:25.550
I'll be the guy in the
eighth row going like this.

01:26.085 --> 01:28.119
Right?!
Right.

01:28.121 --> 01:29.421
Good luck today!
Thank you.

01:29.423 --> 01:31.055
Okay.

01:31.891 --> 01:33.458
Hey, there's the
blushing bride...

01:33.460 --> 01:34.759
Code red!

